data.title: "Casper and the Angels" A Pocket Full O' Schemes/A Tale of Two Trashmen (TV Episode 1979)
data.meta_description: A Pocket Full O' Schemes/A Tale of Two Trashmen: Directed by Oscar Dufau, George Gordon, Ray Patterson, Carl Urbano. With Julie McWhirter, Hal Smith. Mini and Maxi search for a pickpocket called the Snatcher who steals things that he doesn't really want. When they do catch him there is a dispute on who gets the credit.
